    "Hence, it is complicated to perform precise modifications according to user preference, and this limits practical usage.",
    "Later, these limitations are rectified by using the human robot interactions (HRI) models to collect the motion intentions of the humans.",
    "These kinds of systems utilize biosignals like Mechanomyogram (MMG), Electromyogram (EMG), and Electroencephalogram (EEG), which are recorded by placing them in the human body 38.",
    "These bio-signals accomplished highly accurate outcomes and have the human motion intention details to enhance recognition efficiency.",
    "Multiple modalities hold data on various human motions, and the signal-fusing models offer enhanced outcomes."
